"::Shadow Wing::

She flew down to a lower branch.  Still out of his reach, but low 
enough so he could see her.
"Humming birds are small, yes, that is true.  But very quick in the 
wings oh my beloved friend. As you have taught me, not to lose 
yourself in battle. I have tried my best not to get lost in the head. 
I am trying my best to show that even though I can't fight in hand to 
hand combat, I can still help in with the situation. Am I doing a 
good job my beloved?"
She knew her words were having an effect on him. But when she said 
beloved, she meant it. With all her spark, she meant it.
